latestIgtvVideos.title: Full Face of Rare Beauty 🤍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I love what @rarebeauty stands for it’s about not how other people see you, it’s about how you see yourself. I have been loving their products a lot lately. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Products I have used:⁣⁣
Face: ⁣⁣
• Always An Optimist Illuminating Primer⁣⁣
• Liquid Touch Weightless Foundation in shade 230N⁣⁣
• Liquid Touch Brightening Concealer in shade 230N⁣⁣
• Stay Vulnerable Melting Blush in shade Nearly Mauve⁣⁣
• Positive Light Liquid Luminizer in shade Mesmerize ⁣⁣
• Blot & Glow touch up kit⁣⁣
⁣⁣

• Soft Pinch Liquid blush in shade Love & Joy⁣⁣
• Positive Light Liquid Luminizer in shade Mesmerize ⁣⁣

latestIgtvVideos.title: My go-to no makeup look 🕊
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi Guys! 🕊⁣
How are you all doing? I finally filmed my go-to makeup look. I keep on switching products but these are the basics which I always follow for any kind of look I do.⁣
I hope you guys enjoy it, I had so much fun filming this look. ⁣
Products used:⁣
• Primer: @laneigeindia Glowy makeup serum⁣
• Tinted Moisturiser @colourpopcosmetics Hyaluronic tinted moisturizer ⁣
• Brush: @byartis Elite Oval 7⁣
• Concealer: @beccacosmetics Under eye brightening corrector+ @rarebeauty Liquid touch brightening concealer ⁣
• Eyebrows: @benefitindia Goof proof eyebrow pencil⁣
• Brush: Rare Beauty Liquid touch foundation brush ⁣
• Blender: @ybpcosmetics Makeup perfector⁣
• Blush: Rare Beauty Soft pinch liquid blush in shade Joy⁣
• Highlighter: @chanel.beauty Baume Essentiel + @ctilburymakeup Hollywood flawless filter⁣
• Powder: Charlotte Tilbury Airbush Flawless Finish⁣
• Bronzer: Charlotte Tilbury Airbrush Bronzer⁣
• Brush: Wet n Wild Bronzer Brush⁣
• Eyeshadow : @kosas 10 second Eyeshadow in shade Globe⁣
• Mascara: @iliabeauty limitless lash mascara⁣
• Lips: @emcosmetics lip cushion in shade Venetian Rose⁣
• Setting Mist: @lilahbeauty aglow face mist⁣
⁣
